(- Transaction Encoding and Capacity) Tj
T*
(Atho no longer relies on one static tx-size assumption. Effective tx size depends on:) Tj
T*
(- input count,) Tj
T*
(- output count,) Tj
T*
(- amount varint widths,) Tj
T*
(- witness lengths,) Tj
T*
(- optional metadata inclusion.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Current reference witness targets:) Tj
T*
(- Falcon signature: ~666 bytes \(compressed range policy\).) Tj
T*
(- Falcon public key: 897 bytes canonical \(legacy-size acceptance can be policy-gated\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Representative current estimates \(metadata empty, compressed witness, binary sizing path\):) Tj
T*
(- 1 in / 1 out: ~513 vB) Tj
T*
(- 1 in / 2 out: ~566 vB) Tj
T*
(- 2 in / 2 out: ~615 vB) Tj
T*
(- 3 in / 2 out: ~664 vB) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(At 120-second blocks and 2.5M vbytes/block, this maps to approximately:) Tj
T*
(- ~40.6 TPS \(1 in / 1 out\)) Tj
T*
(- ~36.8 TPS \(1 in / 2 out\)) Tj
T*
(- ~33.9 TPS \(2 in / 2 out\)) Tj
T*
(- ~31.4 TPS \(3 in / 2 out\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This supports the target operating band of sustained ~30-35 TPS under realistic mixes.) Tj
T*
