T*
(Atho separates:) Tj
T*
(- **block production security** \(PoW + miner bond\),) Tj
T*
(- **capital participation rewards** \(wallet staking\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This avoids validator-complexity while still adding economic commitment to mining behavior.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
