(- FAQ \(Core\)) Tj
T*
(Q: What is the premine/bootstrap amount, and what is it for?) Tj
T*
(A: Atho currently uses a 50,000 ATHO bootstrap allocation at block 1. Its role is launch) Tj
T*
(bootstrapping: enabling early miner/bond onboarding and predictable network activation before) Tj
T*
(strict BPoW enforcement. It is consensus-accounted and visible on-chain.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Q: Is block 0 treated the same as block 1?) Tj
T*
(A: No. Block 0 is the genesis context. The bootstrap allocation is enforced at block 1, and BPoW) Tj
T*
(enforcement starts at height 100.) Tj
