(Q: What are the most important network parameters to know first?) Tj
T*
(A: 120s block target, 180-block retarget interval, 10 tx confirmations, 150 coinbase maturity,) Tj
T*
(225 atoms/vB fee floor, and BPoW bond requirement 25 ATHO with 25 confirmations.) Tj
T*
() Tj
